    <p>&nbsp;</p>
 <hr>
    --> <p style="margin-bottom:0"><strong>Geophysical Center of the Russian Academy of Sciences</strong> (GC RAS) was established in 1992 with a status of research institute in accordance with the decision of the Presidium of the Russian Academy of Sciences as a result of the reorganization of the Interagency Geophysical Committee (IGC) of RAS established in 1958 by the Decree of the USSR Council of Ministers. <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>The main goal</strong> of the Geophysical Center is to conduct basic and applied research in the field of geophysics and geoinformatics. <br> &nbsp; <strong>Research lines an major tasks: </strong></p> 
                  <ul style="margin-top:0"> 
                   <li>fundamental and applied research in geoinformatics, development of geological and geophysical applications of artificial intelligence methods, geoinformation systems, and GRID systems;</li> 
                   <li>creation of many-layered and multifunctional geoinformation system on the territory of Russia and CIS countries;</li> 
                   <li>providing information for research conducted by the Department of Earth sciences RAS, functioning of the Russian World Data Centers on the Physics of the Solid Earth and Solar-Terrestrial Physics; </li> 
                   <li>creation, maintenance and development of distributed databases, internet resources and knowledge bases on geophysics, geology, space physics and other earth sciences;</li>
                   <li>research in stress and strain, modern crustal movements and rock destruction processes for the purposes of geoecology, seismology, geodynamics and natural risk assessment;</li> 
                   <li>research in geophysical fields and processes in different spheres of the Earth including hydrosphere, ionosphere, near-Earth space and Solar-Terrestrial relations;</li> 
                   <li>elaboration and adaptation of information society technologies to solving problems of geophysics and geoinformatics;</li> 
                   <li>development of new methods of electronic publications and putting them into practice; </li> 
                   <li>creation of international virtual laboratory on electromagnetic monitoring of earthquakes and volcanoes; </li> 
                   <li>execution of functions of the base institution of the Russian National Geophysical Committee and Russian Committee of CODATA.</li> 
                  </ul> 
                  <!-- <img src="images/ppt.gif" width="28" height="29" border="0"> <a href="presentation/GCRAS.ppt" target="_blank">Презентация о ГЦ РАН</a> /--></td> 
